node.text:
This is exactly why I started 🥺
I had a dream and a vision to be able to help as many women as possible from all arround the world to find a healthy and sustainable lifestyle where they feel empowered and confident in their bodies! I never could imagine that I would get so much back from every each and one of you. It is crazy overwhelming to hear testimonials like this. To actually hear your voices and read your stories, I had tears watching this video. 🥺🤍 It fuels me to keep crushing our goals together! 

The You vs. You challenge starts tomorrow the 6th and is as I’ve mentioned before it is totally free to join. You can find all info @ownuapp. 
I hope that we will be thousands of participants just like last year and motivate each other to SLAY these 60 days!

node.text:
I’m absolutely overwhelmed and going into shock over my excitement for this!!!!

the 27th of October is the day I’m launching my very ooowwwwn app, 6pm BST  19.00 CST  19.00 svensk tid
the app will be called OWN|U 😭😭😭

⁠OWN|U will be a subscription-based health and fitness app where I will be able to help you in your daily life like never before. my biggest wish is for you to achieve your goals and creating this is the best way for me to do it. with OWN|U, you will be able to own who you are and want to be. the mission of OWN|U is to help you strive to be the best version of yourself
⁠
in the OWN|U app you will be able to have full access to ALLLLL my current workout guides 🔥 you will also have access to two fresh brandddd new guides releasing with the app, Get Lean, Stay Healthy 2.0 & Get Strong 3.0 

OWN|U will also introduce a bunch of new handy features which will help you immensely in your training. some examples are the new across guides tracking feature, new exercise videos and description, fully functional offline mode, a restart button for full guides and so soooo much more
⁠
many of you have been asking for meal plan options for so long, and with the OWN|U app I can finally deliver it to you!!!! ⭐️
there will be a MEAL LIBRARY with over 100 delicious recipes made by the app’s nutritionist @100kitchenstories
these meals are sorted into diets of standard, vegetarian, vegan and pescatarian. with the fully customizable meal planner you will also be able to plan your nutrition in a very detailed way. to ease your every-day even more, an automated shopping list will be created based on the meals in your meal planner

ONE WEEK LEFT Y’ALL, ONE WEEK!! 😭
THANK YOU for making this happen!!! 
stay tuned during the weeks for more updates and sneak peeks! it’s time to empower yourself and own your body and mind. OWN|U 🤍

node.title: EEEEEK I can finally reveal the app name and launch date 😭🤍

Batwing killeerrrrr! 🔥 Who’s up for the challenge?

This week we’re putting them triceps in focus! How many dips can you do? Want sharp triceps.. DIPS DIPS DIPS! 😄
Really try to lower arms to 90degrees angle. If too heavy with straight legs, bend them a little. But try to push yourself to the max, YOU CAN DO IT! I did 32.

I’m honestly SO HAPPY to see that so any of you are doing my challenge and tagging me!! JOIN the challenge, TAG me & hashtag #hannaoebergchallenge 😍 LET’S GIVE IT EVERYTHING WE HAVE!
Let me know what you think xx

How long can you WALL SIT?

A bit late with the challenge this week, sorry.. honestly, should have recorded this aaaany other day but today 😂.. NOT the best to record AFTER leg day LOLL 😂 I was dyyying!! Deffo doing this in a week again without sore legs!! For those who wants to spice up this challenge, train your legs before haha

Anywhooo... hope you’re ready!?!! How long can you wall sit? KEEP LEGS IN 90degrees 🔥 My time was 3.13 this time.

JOIN the challenge, TAG me & hashtag #hannaoebergchallenge 😍 LET’S GIVE IT EVERYTHING WE HAVE! Remember, struggle makes you stronger.
Let me know what you think xx

Tbh I’m the baddest at making pancakes lol.. 😂 but these never lets me down. They are truly a MUST try. And what better way to start the weekend with if it isn’t with pancakes 🥞 let me know what you think

RECIPE;
2dl almond milk
2 eggs
40g coconut flour (or flour of your taste)
1 scoop @womensbest chocolate vegan protein
1 scoop @womensbest chia seeds
1 tsp cacao
1 tsp baking powder
> MIX ALL INGREDIENTS TOGETHER 🥣
& bake the pancakes from each side. 
Top with berries, fruit, honey or agave syrup, coconut flakes & peanut butter. (or whatever your prefer)
ENJOY! 🥞

node.text:
.
It start NOW! It’s about YOU & and YOUR goals. It’s about YOU and YOUR body. It’s time to make a change. What is 60days compare to what you can learn a long the way and carry with you for the rest of you life? Become the best version of YOU.

Last year I did a 60days challenge that changed my game! I got great results. More then I expected.. but most importantly, I learned how strong I actually am, both body and mind. I got up even though I felt like I was at the bottom. I fought for my goal! 
I wanted to create something for YOU to feel motivated about. Something to work for! The YOU vs. YOU challenge is for us who wants to be a better version on ourselves!

You will not feel motivated every single day‼️ That’s facts. But it’s also normal!! And here’s where the challenge actually challenges you.. to NOT give up on yourself!! To keep going even though it’s though as hell. You keep going, for YOU 🤍
.
HOW DOES IT WORK❓PLZ READ
🔺 Starts at Monday the 6th of January (you can join until Thursday the 9th January)
🔺 It’s total free to join
🔺 To enter; send your before pics/videos (see video) to challenge@hannaoeberg.com before 9th of January
🔺 Write FIRST & LAST NAME in the email
🔺 You don’t have to buy my guides to join
🔺Running until 4th of March. More info before that and when to start taking after pics/video will come close to March
🔺 You will do you best during these 60 days to improve yourself. Either with the knowledge you have. Or with a plan. I will be offering you 25% off my all my guides during 6-9th of January if you want more of my help
🔺 It doesn’t matter what goal you have. Gain weight, loose weight, overall improvement of yourself.. all goals are welcome

MORE INFO in my 🎥 YouTube video on my channel. And also a q&a’s in my story available now!

I know you got this! WE GOT THIS 🤍
BEST OF LUCK! Love you.

node.text:
just here to say hi and wish you a great friday! 

☀️ question? what makes you happy when you’re on vacation?
.. do you train?
.. do you find it hard to rest?
.. do you treat yourself with good food etc.?

a healthy lifestyle should not be surrounded by choices you feel forced to do.. but choices you want for yourself. in my opinion a vacay with no training at all and any type of food you like needs to be accepted as well as those who enjoy to train during their vacation ❤️ do what makes you feel good!

we are really enjoying our family vacation!! Collin is crazy about the water and the water park 😅 love to see him having so much fun!

node.text:
giiiiirls.. IT’S LEG DAY!! 🙃
be sure to hit LIKE and SAVE and try it out yourself ❤️

brrrrutal leg day here we gooo!! 🥴🔥 hear me out.. 6 exercises targeting mostly quads & glutes but also hammies!! if you put all your energy, effort and power into these 6, trust me.. 😏🤌🏼 you’ll be feeling like a million bucks.. or yeah.. maybe not directly after 😂✌🏼

give your workouts a purpose!! why are you in the gym? what’s your goal with this? make your training your good habits not something you’re forced into! ⭐️

❓CURIOUS how many exercises do you do on when training lover body?

METHOD:

1️⃣ Pulse Bulgarian split Squats // 4 set x 8-10 reps each leg
2️⃣ Eccentric Squats // 4 set x 10 reps
3️⃣ BB B-stance hip thrust 3 set x 12 reps each leg
4️⃣ Lying hamstring curl // 4 set x 12 reps
5️⃣ DB goblet squat SUPERSET sissy squat
// 3 set x 10 reps each
6️⃣ Plate side raise // 3 set x 15 reps each leg

come train with me in the @ownuapp
beginner or advanced? home or the gym? WE GOT YOU! 7 days FREE trail 👀 link in bio @hannaoeberg

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by HANNA ÖBERG 🇸🇪 GYM & FITNESS on August 27, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, biceps, people standing and indoor.

node.text:
REAL & RAW workout footage ✊🏼 (here comes a long caption.. sorry 😂 but take a minute and ready this)

here’s my upper body session from earlier this week with Robin. we trained shoulders, chest and tric which is one of my faves to train and especially with him!

I wanna thank you body for allowing me to train and lift heavy. I always respond good to adversities. the struggle makes me feel triggered and all I wanna do is to push my limits. because giving up is not an alternative. I see potential in myself and my body and I think that’s my biggest motivation. I’m not here for the short cuts, I’m in it for the long term.

listen.. I know we all struggle sometimes! but I love that we can talk about it girls ❤️ you’re not alone feeling like you’re in a funk sometimes. that you feel unmotivated and like you wanna give up. taking a rest day instead of working out. we’re all been there… it’s OKEY and some days just needs to be left like that..

- BUT, more importantly, how do we overcome it?? 👊🏼
first of all.. never let your past effect your future! ⭐️ no one can tell you to do something you aren’t committed to do yourself! and no one will do the work for you. either you get the work done or you’re gonna regret it later. when you feel like you wanna give up, what’s your sign to keep going! TRUST ME when I say, you always got 2-3 reps left!! TRY IT. sometimes we can get stuck at counting reps instead of listening to our body. quality over quantity. give your workouts a purpose! all you do is a part of your progress girl ❤️ stay strong, YOU GOT THIS!

the @ownuapp will always be there to support you! whatever goal you have, it will help you find consistency and motivation to keep working on the best version of YOU!

have you ever struggled with these exercises?
simply because we’re all different and sometimes we just need alternatives to get that fire hot pump goinnn okeyyy 😉💪🏼 there’s nothing like “the best exercise” to build quads, glutes, shoulders or whatever… it’s all about your performance and how hard you’re working for what you want ⭐️

.. but sometimes it can feel like there’s a whole jungle out there of great alternatives 🥲.. which there is lol. in this video I thought I brake some of them down for you, hopefully this will help you stay motivated to work on your body and health!
let me know what your think 🔥

1️⃣
cable pull through ➡️ DB banded stiff DL
pull through can be a tricky one so stay with me. keep working on your form, but in the meantime, keep working on your strength by doing DB banded stiff DL

2️⃣
BB front squats ➡️ DB goblet squats
I think we’ve all struggled during BB frontis.. don’t get me wrong, never ever give up on yourself!! this is just an alternative to get use to the movement and build your quad strength up

3️⃣
DB Bulgarian Split squat ➡️ DB assistant Bulgarian Split squat
pure death I KNOW girl!! we allll know. but we are NOT giving up on this one ok. keep pushing! sometimes we just need a little assistance. great for beginners but also fantastic if you just wanna let the focus of the balance go and just rep it out. or if you wanna push the weights weights. many many benefits here

YOU GOT THIS! hope it helps ❤️
Tag a friend 👯‍♀️ that needs this

node.text:
EFFECTIVE LEG DAY 🔥🦵 

I did this;
4 set each exercises x 10-12 reps
rest 60sec between sets

SUPERSET 1:
BB front lunges
BB heel elevate NARROW stance squats

SUPERSET 2:
BB sumo deadlift
BB pulse hip thrusts

SUPERSET 3:
DB stiff DL
DB aside to side lunges

focus quads, glutes & hammies doing only supersets 😜🤙🏼 switch your workout up with this one girls. sometimes 6 exercises is alllll you need 🔥 time effective, fun & challenging!!

SAVE and go get it!!

node.text:
What I wish I knew back then vs. now..
(reposted as my grammar wasn’t feelin it today lol)

1. hours of cardio will not give me the body I want
2. trained 7days /week sometimes + cardio. listen to your body
3. didn’t eat enough food
4. not be afraid of food
5. not compare myself with others 
resulted into me not appreciating myself and how unique my body is
6. appreciate rest days
7. dare to be on a calorie surplus to build muscles

⁉️ WHAT ABOUT YOU GUYS? 😀 what have you learned through your journey?
